---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="High School Sports Banquet Planning Guide" description="Plan unforgettable high school sports banquets, senior nights, award ceremonies, and graduations. Free guides, checklists, and expert planning resources for coaches and parents.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Everything You Need to Plan <span class="highlight">Unforgettable</span> Athletic Celebrations</h1>
      <p>Free expert guides, checklists, and decoration ideas for sports banquets, senior nights, award ceremonies, and graduation parties — built for coaches, by people who've been there.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/banquet-planning/" class="btn btn-primary">Start Planning Your Banquet</a>
        <a href="#guides" class="btn btn-secondary">Explore All Guides</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Strip -->
  <section style="padding:2.5rem 0;background:var(--bg-white);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(180px,1fr));gap:1.5rem;text-align:center;">
        <div><div style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--primary);">10+</div><div class="text-sm text-muted">Free Planning Guides</div></div>
        <div><div style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--primary);">20+</div><div class="text-sm text-muted">Sports Covered</div></div>
        <div><div style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--primary);">8</div><div class="text-sm text-muted">Week Planning Timeline</div></div>
        <div><div style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--primary);">100%</div><div class="text-sm text-muted">Free Resources</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Guide Cards -->
  <section id="guides">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Your Complete Celebration Toolkit</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Four essential guides covering every type of high school athletic celebration, from team banquets to graduation parties.</p>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🏆</div>
          <h3>Sports Banquet Guide</h3>
          <p>Venue selection, menu planning, program structure, seating arrangements, and centerpiece ideas. The complete playbook for a successful banquet.</p>
          <a href="/banquet-planning/" class="card-link">Read the Guide →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">⭐</div>
          <h3>Senior Night Guide</h3>
          <p>Ceremony scripts, parent speech templates, senior gift ideas, and the special moments that make the night unforgettable for seniors and families.</p>
          <a href="/senior-night/" class="card-link">Plan Senior Night →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🎓</div>
          <h3>Graduation Party Guide</h3>
          <p>Themes, catering, decorations, photo booth setups, and party flow planning for your graduate's special celebration.</p>
          <a href="/graduation-party/" class="card-link">Party Planning →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🏅</div>
          <h3>Award Ceremony Guide</h3>
          <p>Award categories, presentation order, coach awards, and creating meaningful moments that recognize every athlete's contribution.</p>
          <a href="/award-ceremony/" class="card-link">Ceremony Planning →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Centerpiece Section -->
  <section class="section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Make Your Tables Unforgettable</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">The right centerpiece transforms a banquet table. Custom 3D printed sports centerpieces capture your team's identity in a way generic decorations never can.</p>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🏈</div>
          <h3>Football</h3>
          <p>8.75", 11.5", and 12" footballs in team colors with optional personalization.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/football-graduation-centerpiece-8-3-4-football" class="card-link" target="_blank">Browse Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🏀</div>
          <h3>Basketball</h3>
          <p>7" and 9" basketballs with team name and player number personalization.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/basketball-banquet-table-centerpiece-7-ball" class="card-link" target="_blank">Browse Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">⚽</div>
          <h3>Soccer</h3>
          <p>8" custom soccer balls designed in your team's colors with personalization.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/custom-soccer-ball-centerpiece-8-soccer-ball-graduation-party-birthday" class="card-link" target="_blank">Browse Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🏐</div>
          <h3>Volleyball</h3>
          <p>8" volleyball centerpieces with full team personalization in multiple color options.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/volleyball-banquet-table-centerpiece-8-volleyball" class="card-link" target="_blank">Browse Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">📣</div>
          <h3>Cheerleading</h3>
          <p>Megaphones and pom pom centerpieces in your squad's colors.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/cheerleader-megaphone-cheer-banquet-table-centerpiece-cheerleading" class="card-link" target="_blank">Browse Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🏃</div>
          <h3>Track & Field</h3>
          <p>Flying track shoes, hurdles, jumps, and javelin designs for track banquets.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/flying-track-shoe-track-shoe-with-wings-banquet-table-centerpiece" class="card-link" target="_blank">Browse Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🏒</div>
          <h3>Hockey</h3>
          <p>Jagged edge player outlines and puck displays in team colors.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/products/hockey-player-centerpiece-unique-jagged-edge-outline-3d-printed-sports-display-8" class="card-link" target="_blank">Browse Options →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">⚾</div>
          <h3>More Sports</h3>
          <p>Browse our full collection of custom centerpieces for every sport.</p>
          <a href="https://lakeshore-gift.myshopify.com/collections/all" class="card-link" target="_blank">Shop All Centerpieces →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sport-Specific Guides -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Sport-by-Sport Banquet Guides</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Every sport has its own traditions and culture. Our sport-specific guides help you plan a celebration that fits your program.</p>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <a href="/sports/football/" class="feature-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="icon-circle">🏈</div>
          <h3>Football Banquets</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Large team logistics, senior night ceremonies, football decoration themes</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/sports/basketball/" class="feature-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="icon-circle">🏀</div>
          <h3>Basketball Banquets</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Intimate team celebrations, hardwood decor, program traditions</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/sports/soccer/" class="feature-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="icon-circle">⚽</div>
          <h3>Soccer Banquets</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Community-style events, combined boys/girls programs</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/sports/volleyball/" class="feature-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="icon-circle">🏐</div>
          <h3>Volleyball Banquets</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Small team celebrations, senior night traditions</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/sports/track/" class="feature-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="icon-circle">🏃</div>
          <h3>Track & Field</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Large team awards, event group recognition</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/sports/cheer/" class="feature-card" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;">
          <div class="icon-circle">📣</div>
          <h3>Cheerleading</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted">Squad-only celebrations, stunt group awards</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-2">
        <a href="/banquet-planning/" class="btn btn-primary">View All Sport Guides →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Free Tools -->
  <section class="section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Free Planning Tools</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Save time and stay organized with our downloadable resources.</p>
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">📋</div>
          <h3>Printable Banquet Checklist</h3>
          <p>Complete 8-week timeline checklist. Print it, share it with your committee, check items off as you go.</p>
          <a href="/checklist/" class="card-link">Get the Checklist →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">💰</div>
          <h3>Budget Worksheet</h3>
          <p>Track every expense from venue to centerpieces. Includes average costs and a grand total summary.</p>
          <a href="/checklist/budget/" class="card-link">Download Worksheet →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">🪑</div>
          <h3>Seating Chart Templates</h3>
          <p>Three seating strategies plus a printable template. Find the right setup for your event.</p>
          <a href="/checklist/seating/" class="card-link">See Templates →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">❓</div>
          <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
          <p>Quick answers to the most common banquet planning questions, curated from real coaches.</p>
          <a href="/faq/" class="card-link">Browse FAQs →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Email Capture -->
  <section style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="email-capture">
        <h3>📥 Get the Free Banquet Planning Checklist</h3>
        <p>Printable PDF with the complete 8-week timeline. Enter your email and we'll send it right over.</p>
        <form action="#" method="post">
          <input type="email" placeholder="Your email address" required />
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send Me the Checklist</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Schema -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebSite",
    "name": "SportsBanquetGuide.com",
    "url": "https://sportsbanquetguide.com",
    "description": "Free guides and resources for planning high school sports banquets, senior nights, award ceremonies, and graduation parties."
  }
  </script>
</MainLayout>
